title: The Age of Innovation for 3D Printing
text:
Expand TCT columnist and one of only a couple of regular speakers at TCT Show + Personalize, Todd Grimm , President, T.A Grimm & Associates, gives this keynote presentation on why we are entering the age of innovation with 3D printing and provides practical advice on leveraging this innovation to push business forward. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
